.banner{style:"background-image: linear-gradient(-180deg, rgba(10,10,10,0.30) 0%, rgba(10,10,10,0.30) 90%), url('images/desk3.jpg')"}
  .container
    %h1 Nathan Kuik
    %h5{class:"thin"} Software Developer
.wrapper-gray
  .container
    .row
      %div{class:"col s10 offset-s1 vertical-margin"}
        %div{class:"card-panel s10 offset-s1 white top-margin center"}
          %h3{id: "about", class:"scrollspy teal-text darken-1"} About
          %p{class:"teal-text darken-1 section flow-text"}
            I'm a former (currently licensed) co-occurring therapist that's shifted into
            tech and web development. I live in Berlin and I love it.
          %p{class:"section scrollspy flow-text teal-text darken-1"}
            I've always been interested in coding, so I took the plunge and completed a 9-week bootcamp through
            = link_to "Le Wagon", "https://www.lewagon.com/", target: "_blank", class:"grey-text text-darken-2"
            and I now work as a developer at
            = link_to "Twyla", "https://www.twylahelps.com/", target: "_blank", class:"grey-text text-darken-2"
            using python to build chatbots.
          %p{class:"flow-text teal-text darken-1"}
            Above all, I'm a problem solver and love to see issues from all possible angles. Finding a solution means getting
            to the root of the problem, and this is what I'm good at.
          %p{class:"flow-text teal-text darken-1"}
            I'm open to ideas and projects, so
            = link_to "send me a message!", "#contact", class:"grey-text text-darken-2"
          = link_to "See my work", "#work", class:"top-margin bottom-margin waves-effect waves-light btn-large teal darken-1"

